<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.hiddencircle.org/view_profile.php?num=78">Splack Dwarf High Priest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kaladornus>kaladornus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 228<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/03 11:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Why AE Taunt?</span><hr size=1> Or for just plain impressing people on lower-level raids.<br>
<br>
