<br>
Just wanted to point out one thing tho...I'm planning on getting it, I am just trying to decide when to get it.  From everything I'd heard, based on my role in the guild, it seemed to me that CA would be the best way for me to go next.  For the 5 points that AE Taunt costs, I could be one point away from CA 2 which I saw as more valuable to my guild.  I was just wondering if there was any uses I may have been overlooking.  Sure, in an xp group I can see the uses all the time, but since my xp seems to come mostly in bursts (I got 4 of the 6 points for ND 3 in one marathon session on Saturday, previously hadn't xped in over a month) I was looking for raid utility.<br>
